action.label: POST_AttachmentContentSet_Base64
action.name: POST_AttachmentContentSet_Base64
action.description: Uploads an attachment to a business object using the file name, mime type of the attachment, business object type, and business object instance key. If the Harmonized Document Management (HDM) functionality is enabled for the business object, then the attachment is created based on the active document type configured for the business object in Customizing. For the operation to be successful, one of the following must be true in Customizing: There must be only one active document type maintained for the business object or there must be a default document type maintained for the business object.
